abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Cornell defeats Harvard, 57-49, in men's action; other men's and women's scores and news noted.
lead_paragraph: Cornell upset Harvard, 57-49, allowing Yale to move into a tie with Harvard for first place in the Ivy League.

headline.main: Cornell Stuns Harvard, Shaking Up Ivy League Race
